VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT mako\.template\.Template\s*\(|chameleon\.PageTemplate\s*\(
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:request\.|input\(|argv|\+ && MISSING:strict_undefined|escape
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects Mako or Chameleon template construction from potentially user-controlled values.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for SSTI: Mako/Chameleon Template Rendering with User Input.
